Feature: Nykaa Shopping Cart
  As a shopper, I want to add products to my cart and proceed to checkout.

Given that a user has access to the Nykaa website
When the user searches for a particular product and adds it to the cart
And the user proceeds to the checkout page and fills in the required details
And the user selects the payment method and confirms the order
Then the order is successfully placed

Scenario: Cancelling the order
Given that a user has an active order on Nykaa website
When the user navigates to the order history section on the website
And the user selects the option to cancel the order
Then the order is successfully cancelled and the user is notified about the cancellation.